      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RIGHT TO RUN (1) hit the frame latest (35.12) when second at this track in a Grade 6/MDN. Has an unbeaten record from this draw, scoring three times. Expected to go close. WHODAT HOOKED (8) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (40.32) in a Other at Murray Bridge. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Should be about the money. BUFFY'S NO ANGEL (2) is having her first run over this longer distance. Comes here a last start placegetter at this track in Grade 6 (31.08). Can hit the frame with the right run. MARLI MOO (5) collected a minor prize last start and ran time in the process - must be considered.",
